Package: EZtrack
Type: Package
Title: Easy Tools for Importing, Visualizing, and Summarizing Animal Tracking Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "YourFirstName", 
           family = "YourLastName", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"), 
           email = "your@email.com")
Description: 
    Provides a simple and consistent interface for working with animal tracking data. 
    Includes functions to import and clean tracking datasets from common formats (CSV, Excel, Movebank), 
    visualize movement tracks using interactive Leaflet maps, 
    and compute useful summary statistics per individual. 
    Designed for ease of use with support for spatial objects via the 'sf' package.
